Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_srt

The shadow RX trigger register is a shadow register for the RX trigger bits (MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR[RXTRIG]) that can be used to remove the burden of having to store the previously written value to MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR in memory and having to mask this value so that only the RX trigger bits get updated.
